<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BCA Admission - Bangalore University</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-purple-100 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center font-sans">

  <div class="bg-white max-w-3xl w-full p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-blue-700 mb-6">BCA Admission Portal â€“ 2025</h1>

    <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Welcome to the official admission portal for <strong>Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA)</strong> at Bangalore University.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Instructions to Fill the Application Form:</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Click the "Fill Application Form" button below to begin the application process.</li>
      <li>Fill all required fields in the online form carefully.</li>
      <li>After submission, you will receive a unique <strong>Application Number</strong>. Keep it safe for future reference and counselling.</li>
      <li>Take a <strong>printout</strong> of the filled application form.</li>
      <li>Paste your <strong>passport-size photograph</strong> on the printed form (do not upload online).</li>
      <li>Submit the printed form <strong>physically at the university</strong> along with the required documents for verification.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
      Note: If any false information is found, the application is liable to be cancelled at any stage.
    </p>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/apply" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Fill Application Form
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
